description: The Crab Cab is a 5 Star mobile "restaurant" on wheels that is nevertheless affordable! This truck uses the freshest ingredients to create delectable soups, and sumptuous "finger-licking" crab cakes. But the menu doesn't stop there! It also includes succulent hickory-smoked salmon that literally melts in your mouth. Hungry for a bite? Just make sure when you see the signature yellow and black checkerboard logo with Mr. Crabby on it with his shades on that you hail it to stop like a New York City Cab. You will be glad that you did.
name: The Crab Cab
